<plot>The plight of a young man caught between the traditional ways of his immigrant Indian parents and the freer lifestyle of his American peers. Working in his parent's convenience store, Ravi flirts with a seductive classmate all the while his parents are hatching a proper arranged marriage for him. But Ravi's high spirits are not to be cramped by his austere parents. Captures the experience of second generation immigrants in a multicultural society.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?576866</url></doc>
